svg.title: A set of six figures, labelled “Fig. 23” through “Fig. 28,” showing a variety of arcane drawings. Fig. 24, for example, is a drawing of a parrot, a pile of three stones, a church, a key and a swaddled infant. Fig. 25 shows two variants of a drawing of a heart pierced by arrows and/or nails. The other figures include drawings of things such as a knot, numbered arrows, a hand, and a book.
